<paragraph blockId="11.[144,1104,279,335]" pageId="11" pageNumber="2562">
Twenty-four specimens were collected from 
<collectingRegion box="[664,870,279,303]" country="China" name="Yunnan" pageId="11" pageNumber="2562">Yunnan Province</collectingRegion>
, 
<materialsCitation location="Guizhou Province" pageId="11" pageNumber="2562" specimenCount="16" stateProvince="Guizhou">
<specimenCount box="[885,1037,279,303]" pageId="11" pageNumber="2562" type="generic">16 specimens</specimenCount>
from 
<collectingRegion box="[144,354,311,335]" country="China" name="Guizhou" pageId="11" pageNumber="2562">Guizhou Province</collectingRegion>
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="11.[144,243,383,407]" box="[144,243,383,407]" pageId="11" pageNumber="2562">
<emphasis box="[144,243,383,407]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="2562">Remarks</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="11.[144,1104,423,511]" pageId="11" pageNumber="2562">
This species was reported as new for science from 
<collectingRegion box="[707,946,423,447]" country="China" name="Guangdong" pageId="11" pageNumber="2562">Guangdong Province</collectingRegion>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Pilato G" box="[961,1093,423,447]" pageId="11" pageNumber="2562" pagination="59 - 68" refId="ref6149" refString="Pilato G. 1974. Tre nuove specie di Tardigradi muscicoli di Cina. Animalia. 1: 59 - 68." type="journal article" year="1974">Pilato 1974</bibRefCitation>
). It was subsequently reported from Xijiang Uigur Autonomous Region (
<bibRefCitation author="Beasley CW &amp; Miller WR" pageId="11" pageNumber="2562" pagination="49 - 55" refId="ref5812" refString="Beasley CW, Miller WR. 2007. Tardigrada of Xinjiang Uygur autonomous region, China. J Limnol. 66 (Suppl. 1): 49 - 55." type="journal article" year="2007">Beasley and Miller 2007</bibRefCitation>
). This is the first report of this species from the Yunnan-Guizhou Plateau.
</paragraph>
